   <title>
    摘美國最大變裝實境秀后冠 妮妃雅寫台灣第一人紀錄
   </title>
   <description>
    <![CDATA[<img src="https://images.weserv.nl/?n=-1&url=https%3A%2F%2Fnews-data.pts.org.tw%2Fmedia%2F199459%2Fconversions%2Fcover-webp.webp" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">   
                                            <div class="articleimg">美國實境電視節目「魯保羅變裝皇后秀」（RuPaul's Drag Race）最新一季決賽結果出爐，來自台灣的妮妃雅拿下象徵冠軍的「下一個美國變裝巨星」（America's Next Drag Superstar）頭銜，成為該節目自2009年開播以來首位封后的台灣選手。而他接下來還將代表台灣，在巴黎奧運登台演出。</div>
                                        <p>曾經獲頒艾美獎肯定的美國實境電視節目「魯保羅變裝皇后秀」，最新一季決賽結果於台灣時間20日出爐，由來自台灣的妮妃雅（Nymphia Wind）拿下象徵該節目后冠的頭銜「下一個美國變裝巨星」，成為節目開播16年以來首位拿下冠軍的台灣人。</p><div class="raw-html-embed"><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C59-AWoJTsB/?utm_source=ig_embed&utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:540px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"> <a href="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C59-AWoJTsB/?utm_source=ig_embed&utm_campaign=loading" style=" background:#FFFFFF; line-height:0; padding:0 0; text-align:center; text-decoration:none; width:100%;" target="_blank"> <div style=" display: flex; flex-direction: row; align-items: center;"> <div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div> <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"> <div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div> <div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div> <div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,5